description.value: $MARKs are the currency of the Education Economy. For all of modern history schooling was seen as a kind of charity service for humanity. we sent kids to work at school for 8+ hours a day, they earned nothing tangible and they received nothing tangible. Now with $Mark students will be PAID for their work (studying). They will learn valuable money management skills and personal accountability from a young age.
